---
// Hero — the pitch
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <span class="eyebrow">Sylents · electric jet propulsion</span>
    <h1>The first jet<br />for broad leisure use.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Jets were hard to handle. Until now. Silent, light, nothing moving outside — the jet, finally usable.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn">Request a demo</a>
      <a href="#products" class="btn btn-ghost">See the drive</a>
    </div>
    <div class="spec-strip">
      <div><strong>1–10 kW</strong><span>power range</span></div>
      <div><strong>14.6 kg</strong><span>incl. battery</span></div>
      <div><strong>50 min</strong><span>full load</span></div>
      <div><strong>0</strong><span>moving parts outside</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.hero {
  padding-block: var(--spacing-80) var(--spacing-70);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.12), transparent 60%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-inner { position: relative; max-width: 820px; }
.hero h1 {
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.hero-sub {
  font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.5vw, 1.35rem);
  color: var(--color-text-main);
  max-width: 600px;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.hero-cta {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
}
.spec-strip {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 1.5rem;
  padding: 1.5rem 0;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}
.spec-strip > div {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.spec-strip strong {
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  color: var(--color-light);
  line-height: 1;
}
.spec-strip span {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  margin-top: 0.35rem;
}
@media (max-width: 720px) {
  .spec-strip { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; }
}
</style>
